A market [[exchange|currency_exchange]] site serving those trading between bitcoins and Euro (EUR).

##Deposits

###BTC
Bitcoins funds are added to the account after six confirmations.

###EUR
EUR bank transfers (SEPA) are accepted for deposits at no charge by the exchange.

###International wire
Dollars (USD) and Euro (EUR) may be sent as either an international or domestic (U.S.) wire transfer. Currency conversion fees may apply.

##Selling Bitcoins

Withdrawal methods supported are SEPA (EUR) and International Bank Wire Transfer (EUR only). 

##History

The service launched publicly  (7.1).  Kraken is operated by Payward, Inc. of California, USA.

